       ======================================================       
       | GDB_PROCESSOR INFRASTRUCTURE SOFTWARE DISTRIBUTION |
       ======================================================
                            Version 1.0

  Install by running 'python setup.py install --prefix=${HOME}/opt'   
     from the root directory (i.e. from directory gdb_processor)

  !!-------------------------------------------------------------!!
  !!  The option --prefix=${HOME}/opt is critical: workflow is   !!
  !!  designed to be dependent on this file structure, even      !!
  !!  though it is machine-independent (he says with confidence) !!
  !!-------------------------------------------------------------!!


----------------------------------------------------------------------
|    DIRECTORY    |       CONTENTS       |        DESCRIPTION        |
|=================|======================|===========================|
|                 |  workflow_helper.py  | Python module to handle   |
|                 |                      |  creation of working dirs |
|      root       |----------------------|---------------------------|
|                 |       setup.py       |    Python setup script    |
|                 |                      |        (see above)        |
|-----------------|----------------------|---------------------------|
|                 |    lvalertlisten     |                           |
|                 |     plot_allsky      |     scripts called by     |    
|                 |   plot_xcorrelate    |     (xy)_processor.py     |
|       bin       |     dqtolabel.py     |                           |
|                 |----------------------|---------------------------|
|                 | lowmass_processor.py |  scripts called directly  | <--- Writes and submits condor 
|                 | exttrig_processor.py |  in response to LV Alert  | <--- .dag and .sub files to 
|-----------------|----------------------|---------------------------|      handle the relevant jobs
|                 |  lvalertconfig.ini   |                           |
|                 |  lowmass_config.ini  |    configuration files    | <--- Defines certain variables
|       etc       |  exttrig_config.ini  |                           |      in the processor scripts
|                 |----------------------|---------------------------|
|                 |  lvalertlisten.sub   | LVAlert listener sub file | <--- This is what gets submitted
|-----------------|----------------------|---------------------------|      to initiate the LV listener
|                 |                      | Package containing python |
|                 |      __init__.py     | modules useful in proces- |
|                 |                      | sing gravitational-wave   |
|                 |                      | and exttrig events        |
|                 |----------------------|---------------------------|
|                 |                      |  Module contains classes  |
| gracedb_events  |      ExtTrig.py      |  whose attributes are     | 
|                 |                      |  specific to external     |
|                 |                      |  triggers                 |
|                 |----------------------|---------------------------|
|                 |                      | Module contains classes   |
|                 |       GraCE.py       | whose attributes are      | 
|                 |                      | specific to gravitational |
|                 |                      | wave candidate events     |
----------------------------------------------------------------------


